    ArrivalProcess produces the time when next customer arrivals.
    Clock

    Engine implement three-phase simulator.

    Event holds three-phase simulation event information; type and time of the event.
    EventList
    Eventlist holds events according to time of the event.
    IEventType
    Interface to make the simulator engine independent of the event type, i.e., it is possible to use different event enumerations without modifying the core of the simulator.
